msgid ""
"Open the device (`see coreboot docs "
"<https://doc.coreboot.org/mainboard/lenovo/Ivy_Bridge_series.html>`__) "
"and make sure you can access both flash chips."
msgstr ""
"Abrir o dispositivo (` ver docs coreboot "
"<https://doc.coreboot.org/mainboard/lenovo/Ivy_Bridge_series.html>`__) e "
"certificar-se de que pode aceder a ambos os chips flash."

